com.metreeca.link

Interface Toolkit

  • Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface Toolkit
    Linked data toolkit.

    Toolkits enable linked data applications to provide custom shared tools or to override standard platform-provided tools with custom plugins.

    Custom toolkits listed in the com.metreeca.link.Tookit service loader provider configuration file in the META-INF/services/ resource directory of an application will be automatically loaded by server adapters.
